rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0001
rows.name:
You know Superbians are the next
most common race in Avaritia
after the Nopon, right?

rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0002
rows.name:
There are quite a few people like me
who were born in Superbia but
choose to live here instead.

rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Main reason for that is, Superbia's
Divine Beast isn't an easy place to live.

rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0004
rows.name:
The ground is barren, and not many
crops grow there.

rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Some choose to move to Gula too,
but I went for Avaritia since there
are more working opportunities.

rows.label: tlk45300054_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Though I guess the bigger reason is that
I failed to get into the Superbian army.
